<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>166</hymn_number>
<author>Duma</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damlai gamgaw a ka zin sung hin.
 Nicheng lungkham leh gitloh nate'n;
 Lawpna a chawlhsak ngaiin Lalpa kapin ka sam
 Tuhin vangsakna a lang tai

[V2]
 Aw, a chawlh ding chu phal kin, (2)
 Ngaiin Lalpa sam zaw diek hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Babulon sala na tanghaw chun,
 Lungkham, kapin Zion a thil ui,
 A kingkang gi hawih chawla lungkhama kaphaw chu
 A Lal Jehovin a puidawk

[V4]
 Kipaka Zion la sa'n (2)
 Kipakin Lalpa chu pakchai tiu.

[V5]
 3. Thagau, sem hatin a hun nai puoi,
 Buoi leh chapo, gimtheih na haw hi;
 Sem hatin Lalpa Na hatna leh Na theihna chun,
 Thim thilbawl haw hung kilang hen.

[V6]
 Thim thilbawl sumang hen la (2)
 Lalpa, Na min mai hi hung hawih hen.

[V7]
 4. Thagau, ka hun ngai ui ei puiin,
 Gitloh leh manthaina gam ahin;
 Na lampi hawh dan ka hethiem puoi, ka Lal Isu
 Ka lam thuom chengah na dingin.

[V8]
 Gam lopi ka tun masieh (2)
 Vangsakna khutin ei pui zelin.</lyrics>
<title>Zion La Lemin</title>
</song>